{"tid":327324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「記住！！~」Trivago 個男人係咪紀曉嵐扮??","createTime":"2017-07-18T16:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T11:49:57.000Z","uid":24160,"like":19,"dislike":282,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36117957702228da588e23e7549eacdba9f2bb00","tid":327324,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/axKtkDt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaxKtkDt.jpg&h=ef6881f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住!</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d2b90w9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd2b90w9.gif&h=f95f7a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrivago顯示嘅係同一間酒店房有唔同網站提供嘅價錢<br />\n所以先可以用至抵價錢搵到啱你心水嘅酒店"},{"pid":"16013f411c3d5649d89800ef847692ab8727497f","tid":327324,"uid":22858,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"賣廣告賣到咁無禮貌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba02665dbe62c99e3dfd230ac3441be9df680d4f","tid":327324,"uid":24160,"like":30,"dislike":9,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:14:59.000Z","msg":"你有冇試過上網搵酒店?<br />\n有冇發現同一間酒店房有好多唔同嘅價錢?<br />\nTrivago 即時幫你比較全球250個網站同應同程式<br />\n超過一百萬間酒店嘅價格<br />\n你唔使再㗰時間同捱貴酒店<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QYLtR45.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQYLtR45.gif&h=b66e97a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrivago幫你用至抵價錢搵到啱你心水嘅酒店<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Sh23t8d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSh23t8d.gif&h=821c4af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上Trivago網站輸入目的地<br />\n揀返check in 同埋 check out 日期<br />\n再撳搜尋! 就係咁簡單~<br />\nTrivago 喺眾多個網站同埋應用程式當中<br />\n幫你搵出最受歡迎嘅酒店<br />\n你可以跟返你嘅budget嚟調整價錢, 選擇酒店星級,<br />\n或者按照超過一億個用家評分嚟篩選酒店。<br />\n記住!<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d2b90w9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd2b90w9.gif&h=f95f7a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTrivago顯示嘅係同一間酒店房有唔同網站提供嘅價錢<br />\n所以先可以用至抵價錢搵到啱你心水嘅酒店<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OQUffMT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOQUffMT.gif&h=073670ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n酒店? Trivago!"},{"pid":"888d56635ff3a4caa878001a7d843b5d6998a0ca","tid":327324,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"個男人叫做黎學勤<br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jefferylai/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjefferylai%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=261dacab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jefferylai/?hl=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"4e0a424bcaace5c43a48afd26948a4299a767081","tid":327324,"uid":24160,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"佢煩啲定係車熟霉煩啲?<br />\n​<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7m3mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7m3mv.jpg&h=33132a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n考試面試見客演講決策<br />\n你同我每日都會面對<br />\n咁係呢啲咁重要既時刻<br />\n究竟我地點樣可以保持冷靜<br />\n迎接每一個難關呢<br />\n淑梅姐 你有啲咩對策可以應付啊<br />\n其實呢好多時係開 mic 啊做 show 之前我都會好緊張㗎<br />\n直至到我用左英國巴哈急救寧<br />\n佢係種天然既鎮靜劑嚟㗎<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/CMrrzki.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FCMrrzki.gif&h=a36df928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食一粒之後呢<br />\n好快情緒就會冷靜落嚟<br />\n精神自然更加集中啦<br />\n特別果啲考試啊面試啊見客之前呢<br />\n食一粒幫助佢地舒緩情緒<br />\n面對挑戰<br />\n呢個產品啊係英國已經有成七十幾年歷史㗎喇<br />\n成分天然安全可靠<br />\n大人小朋友都啱用㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Wb40tOP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FWb40tOP.gif&h=4251cdeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就連英國皇室都用緊添㗎<br />\n另外呢我想問下楊校長<br />\n壓力呢又會影響睡眠喎<br />\n其實可以點樣處理啊<br />\n其實工作真係好繁忙㗎<br />\n返到屋企仲 住學校既工作<br />\n就搞到夜晚訓唔著<br />\n自從用左英國巴哈甜睡寧<br />\n只要臨瞓之前係脷底噴兩下<br />\n好快就訓著<br />\n夜晚仲唔會紮醒添<br />\n佢成分天然<br />\n加上百栗花既精華<br />\n好快就令我地鬆弛神經<br />\n促進我地既深層睡眠<br />\n佢無副作用<br />\n亦都唔會造成依賴<br />\n咁我哋瞓醒覺<br />\n第二日就能夠精神奕奕咁繼續工作㗎喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zujAP31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzujAP31.jpg&h=37e8223b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e2a83a5dedb477bc769989feec7c1c7acb143b1","tid":327324,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"呢條麻甩佬好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75723576b91944e347e15b06b9c91dbb6df2083f","tid":327324,"uid":47480,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"驗眼啦"},{"pid":"e619e0fecf128718b0fdc583157d9afb3a758ec4","tid":327324,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"我女朋友 個朋友 fd，見過真人，幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目測有180高，佢條女都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同佢條女都係舞蹈出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa7c888844a9c5775bac09b8bc724aa3573bf05","tid":327324,"uid":13678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"聽緊歌都聽到把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8e1e8cb847b4d413fea4228acb7ae998cb4b31","tid":327324,"uid":14244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"呢個好過之前條白痴妹<br />\n慳個幾十好似中咗獎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2285a172877dd7d56f7d7f581d4c63f0302ef84","tid":327324,"uid":72730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:40:03.000Z","msg":"個po有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal